Text: Thanks for these uploads.A lot of guys stuck on 6%.If you don't know how to check it, then first open your torrent client , click on seeding file,see in the ''Detailed info Box'',if it does not show there,then press F5 (for utorrent) ,you'll see a box at the bottom,where you can check different statistics for every active torrent,including peers.You can see no one has complete copy of this book,i.e 100%.
